<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:09:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队加入辛贝特对约旦河西岸犹太恐怖主义的警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-joins-shin-bet-warning-over-jewish-terrorism-in-west-bank/00000191-9e2f-d453-ab9f-feafbdcf0000</link><description>军方表示，约旦河西岸犹太人定居点的领导层几乎没有采取任何行动来遏制暴力行为，辛贝特安全部门也表示，暴力行为“对以色列造成了难以形容的损害”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 13:53:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-joins-shin-bet-warning-over-jewish-terrorism-in-west-bank/00000191-9e2f-d453-ab9f-feafbdcf0000</guid></item><item><title>政府宁愿忽视以色列经济的 5 个令人震惊的警告信号</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/5-alarming-warning-signs-for-israels-economy-that-the-government-is-ignoring/00000191-9e01-d824-abd7-feabf3f70000</link><description>过去几周的数据引发了人们对以色列经济未来的严重担忧。政府有行动的工具，却忙于内讧和挑衅</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 12:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/5-alarming-warning-signs-for-israels-economy-that-the-government-is-ignoring/00000191-9e01-d824-abd7-feabf3f70000</guid></item><item><title>拉皮德：内塔尼亚胡对十月前感到“无聊、漠不关心”。联合简报期间发出 7 项警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/lapid-netanyahu-was-bored-indifferent-to-pre-oct-7-warnings-during-joint-briefing/00000191-9da1-da8a-a991-bfe514450000</link><description>拉皮德在政府拒绝组建正式委员会后成立的民事调查小组作证说，内塔尼亚胡的高级军事助手表示，恐怖组织认为以色列的软弱是由于司法改革带来的社会动荡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 12:21:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/lapid-netanyahu-was-bored-indifferent-to-pre-oct-7-warnings-during-joint-briefing/00000191-9da1-da8a-a991-bfe514450000</guid></item><item><title>获救人质证实阿里·扎尔马诺维奇在加沙被关押期间被谋杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/rescued-hostage-says-arye-zalmanovich-was-murdered-in-captivity-while-held-together/00000191-9de8-d172-abd9-ffff6a8b0000</link><description>周三，凯德·法尔汉·卡迪从哈马斯的囚禁中被救出。他告诉在囚禁期间被谋杀的阿里耶·扎尔马诺维奇的儿子，他们在加沙建立了特殊的纽带</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 12:17:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/rescued-hostage-says-arye-zalmanovich-was-murdered-in-captivity-while-held-together/00000191-9de8-d172-abd9-ffff6a8b0000</guid></item><item><title>目击者称，蒙面以色列军队和警察袭击约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/masked-israeli-army-and-police-forces-attack-palestinians-in-west-bank-eyewitnesses-say/00000191-9874-dd8c-addd-b9f4f7ca0000</link><description>一名目击者称，他们“戴着面具，穿着制服，但没有任何名牌或随身摄像机”。目击者补充说，部队指控这群人属于哈马斯，给其中一人戴上手铐，殴打他，并将他扔进河里；以色列国防军和边防警察表示现场没有部队</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 11:58:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/masked-israeli-army-and-police-forces-attack-palestinians-in-west-bank-eyewitnesses-say/00000191-9874-dd8c-addd-b9f4f7ca0000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷发现第一圣殿时期的古代印章，印有亚述恶魔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-08-29/ty-article-magazine/ancient-seal-featuring-assyrian-demon-from-first-temple-period-discovered-in-jerusalem/00000191-9d73-d383-abb7-9d7f89cb0000</link><description>考古学家称，一块用古希伯来语刻有“LeYeho´ezer ben Hosh´ayahu”名字的黑石印章护身符显示了新亚述帝国对古代犹大国的文化影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 11:00:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-08-29/ty-article-magazine/ancient-seal-featuring-assyrian-demon-from-first-temple-period-discovered-in-jerusalem/00000191-9d73-d383-abb7-9d7f89cb0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道伊朗准备对以色列进行报复袭击，美国加强了中东军事存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/concerned-about-iranian-revenge-attack-u-s-keeps-two-aircraft-carriers-in-region/00000191-953f-d302-add5-9fbf55cd0000</link><description>尽管以色列本周挫败了真主党的袭击，但拜登政府正在加强其在该地区的空中和海上力量，同时向以色列紧急运送武器，因为人们越来越担心伊朗对德黑兰刺杀哈马斯领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚进行报复</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 10:36:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/concerned-about-iranian-revenge-attack-u-s-keeps-two-aircraft-carriers-in-region/00000191-953f-d302-add5-9fbf55cd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队报告称，在正在进行的大规模行动中，五名西岸武装分子在清真寺内被击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reports-killing-five-west-bank-militants-amid-ongoing-large-scale-operation/00000191-9d2f-dffe-a9b7-df3f5efb0000</link><description>军方称，遇难者中有一名伊斯兰圣战组织高级成员，他负责最近一次导致一名以色列平民死亡的袭击事件。巴勒斯坦卫生部报告自行动开始以来已有 12 人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 08:50:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reports-killing-five-west-bank-militants-amid-ongoing-large-scale-operation/00000191-9d2f-dffe-a9b7-df3f5efb0000</guid></item><item><title>随着恐怖活动的加剧和以色列右翼的火上浇油，约旦河西岸正处于爆炸的边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/with-terror-on-the-rise-and-israels-right-fanning-the-flames-the-west-bank-could-explode/00000191-9a88-d712-adff-bf9e84640000</link><description>更多的恐怖警告、极端主义定居者的袭击以及本格维尔对阿克萨清真寺的挑衅正在使约旦河西岸达到沸点。 尽管以色列在营救一名以色列贝都因人质后加大了对哈马斯的军事压力，但辛瓦尔在谈判中仍然坚定不移</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 03:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/with-terror-on-the-rise-and-israels-right-fanning-the-flames-the-west-bank-could-explode/00000191-9a88-d712-adff-bf9e84640000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列-哈马斯协议调解人将试图主导加沙走廊争议的解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/gaza-deal-mediators-to-float-new-proposal-within-days-to-resolve-border-control-issues/00000191-9a4d-d510-adb7-9edd65470000</link><description>周三在卡塔尔开始的谈判中，美国和其他斡旋国家预计将在“几天内”就费城和内扎里姆走廊的控制提出一项新提案</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 03:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/gaza-deal-mediators-to-float-new-proposal-within-days-to-resolve-border-control-issues/00000191-9a4d-d510-adb7-9edd65470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队加入辛贝特对约旦河西岸犹太恐怖主义的警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article-live/un-chief-urges-israel-to-end-west-bank-operation-as-death-toll-climbs-to-11/00000191-9be9-d510-adb7-9ff93cb30000</link><description>欧盟最高外交官要求制裁鼓吹战争罪的以色列部长 ■ 以色列军队报告称，在正在进行的大规模行动中打死了五名约旦河西岸武装分子 ■ 人质家属在加沙边境集会寻求达成协议 ■ 来自尼尔奥兹的 86 岁阿耶·扎尔马诺维奇 (Arye Zalmanovich) 被杀与本周获救的凯德·法尔汉·卡迪在加沙被扣为人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 02:24:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-29/ty-article-live/un-chief-urges-israel-to-end-west-bank-operation-as-death-toll-climbs-to-11/00000191-9be9-d510-adb7-9ff93cb30000</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰外交官：内塔尼亚胡在与泽连斯基的通话中称赞乌克兰防空</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/ukrainian-diplomat-netanyahu-lauded-ukrainian-air-defense-in-call-with-zelenskyy/00000191-9a8f-d396-a59d-ffdfdc140000</link><description>泽伦斯基发言人表示，在两国领导人自十月以来的首次通话中，以色列总理“表达了对乌克兰主权和领土完整的支持”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 20:38:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/ukrainian-diplomat-netanyahu-lauded-ukrainian-air-defense-in-call-with-zelenskyy/00000191-9a8f-d396-a59d-ffdfdc140000</guid></item><item><title>美国会因为本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇试图点燃中东而制裁他们吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-28/ty-article/.highlight/will-the-u-s-hold-ben-gvir-smotrich-accountable-for-trying-to-set-the-mideast-on-fire/00000191-9a0e-d290-a5b3-fe9e8c690000</link><description>新一轮制裁，加上针对极右翼以色列部长的日益敌对的公开言论，表明本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇仍然是美国官员心目中的首要人物，旨在避免中东发生任何进一步的危机</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 19:48:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-28/ty-article/.highlight/will-the-u-s-hold-ben-gvir-smotrich-accountable-for-trying-to-set-the-mideast-on-fire/00000191-9a0e-d290-a5b3-fe9e8c690000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日被杀并被带到加沙的以色列国防军士兵遗体已返回以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/body-of-soldier-killed-on-october-7-and-taken-to-gaza-returned-to-israel-idf-announces/00000191-9a2d-df2d-a3bd-babdc0e40000</link><description>根据家人的要求，遗体被送回以色列的阵亡士兵的身份尚未公布</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 19:09:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/body-of-soldier-killed-on-october-7-and-taken-to-gaza-returned-to-israel-idf-announces/00000191-9a2d-df2d-a3bd-babdc0e40000</guid></item><item><title>“生命的价值正在崩溃”：抗议车队驶往加沙呼吁达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/value-of-life-is-crumbling-protest-convoy-drives-to-gaza-calling-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-9a0a-dffe-a9b7-db3af4ae0000</link><description>以色列人质家属在特拉维夫集会，然后随车队前往贝埃里基布兹，在那里他们猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡坚持加沙边界问题，破坏了人质协议谈判。失去亲人的母亲说：“我很抱歉，费城路线比人质更重要”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 18:58:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/value-of-life-is-crumbling-protest-convoy-drives-to-gaza-calling-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-9a0a-dffe-a9b7-db3af4ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队调查发现定居者对巴勒斯坦村庄的袭击是“恐怖行为”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-probe-finds-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village-a-terrorist-act/00000191-99ce-d975-a9f3-bfffdff90000</link><description>中央司令部司令说：“这是以色列人发动的最严重的恐怖袭击，我们因没有更早到达并保护他们而失败”</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 17:42:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-probe-finds-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village-a-terrorist-act/00000191-99ce-d975-a9f3-bfffdff90000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日遇难者家属不允许在国家仪式上“愤世嫉俗地使用”他们的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/ex-hostages-oct-7-victims-families-deny-cynical-use-of-loved-ones-names-for-ceremony/00000191-9959-d222-a797-9f5f56d70000</link><description>他们要求不要提及他们亲人的名字，也不要“以任何身份”展示他们的照片。内塔尼亚胡的一位盟友告诉媒体，总理的“仇恨者”想要一个“替代国家”，仪式的领导人、交通部长米里·雷格夫表示，尽管有“噪音”，她仍将继续前进</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 17:09:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/ex-hostages-oct-7-victims-families-deny-cynical-use-of-loved-ones-names-for-ceremony/00000191-9959-d222-a797-9f5f56d70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第327天：美国制裁西岸激进定居点的安全负责人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-327-u-s-sanctions-security-chief-of-radical-west-bank-settlement/00000191-99d8-dffe-a9b7-dbfaa0180001</link><description>以色列代表团启程前往卡塔尔继续停火谈判，一位消息人士称，如果费城走廊和拉法过境点没有灵活性，“我们能否确保人质获释值得怀疑” ■ 以色列国防军公布对定居者的调查结果本月早些时候发生的骚乱导致一名巴勒斯坦人死亡，以色列国防军称，警方从辛贝特那里获得了情报，应该采取行动 ■ 这是战争开始 327 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 16:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-327-u-s-sanctions-security-chief-of-radical-west-bank-settlement/00000191-99d8-dffe-a9b7-dbfaa0180001</guid></item><item><title>从哈马斯囚禁中获救的以色列人质回家庆祝他小儿子的一岁生日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-rescued-from-hamas-captivity-is-home-for-his-youngest-sons-first-birthday/00000191-989e-d222-a797-9e9fc2ac0000</link><description>以色列国防军部队在一个地下大院进行搜查后，人们普遍怀疑哈马斯人质可能就藏在那里，凯德·法尔汉·卡迪被单独找到。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 14:45:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-rescued-from-hamas-captivity-is-home-for-his-youngest-sons-first-birthday/00000191-989e-d222-a797-9e9fc2ac0000</guid></item><item><title>“生活就像地狱”：约旦河西岸旅游之都伯利恒变成鬼城</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/life-has-been-hell-inside-bethlehem-the-west-banks-tourism-capital-turned-ghost-town/00000191-97e9-d13a-ab93-dfff37850000</link><description>巴勒斯坦城市伯利恒每年都会接待多达 150 万名游客。以色列-加沙战争对其造成了毁灭性影响，游客纷纷远离，出租车司机称他们平均每天的收入相当于一包香烟</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 14:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/life-has-been-hell-inside-bethlehem-the-west-banks-tourism-capital-turned-ghost-town/00000191-97e9-d13a-ab93-dfff37850000</guid></item></channel></rss>